1. ng new my-lib-app
2. cd my-lib-app
3. ng g library my-lib
4. Add what you want to add in the module.
5. ng build my-lib
6. test it with unit-test or in your my-lib-app.
7. npm publish -- that will publish your library onto npm.
   Before that you should run npm login, with your npm account.
   1) Remove the private attribute in package.json.
   2) cd dist/my-lib
   3) npm publish
8. Install your library in your app.
